      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm parting ways with my absolute dream of a car, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total beauty. It\u2019s in truly spectacular shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just left the dealership! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is the one. I'm super excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
