    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example maintains its factory-spec mechanical integrity, including a precision-shifted Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains rigid with documented subframe reinforcement, and the dual-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal valve timing and linear torque delivery. Performance is bolstered by the original suspension geometry and cross-drilled rotors. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist seeking uncompromised driving dynamics and mechanical perfection.",
