      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in true showroom condition. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time capsule' state: the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-resolution infotainment system to the ambient lighting\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, backed by a comprehensive, single-owner service history and a recent gold-standard multi-point inspection. No leaks, no rattles, and a strictly smoke-free/pet-free interior. This is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
